           <script>
            function SetCookie (region, name, setvisited) {
                   if (region != "blankchildrens") {
                       var regionval = ReadCookie(name);
 
                       if (!regionval) {
                          CreateCookie(name, region, 1000);
                       }
                       else {
                          EraseCookie(name);
                          CreateCookie(name, region, 1000);
                       }
 
                       document.location = "/" + region;
                   }
               }
               function EraseCookie (name) {
                  CreateCookie(name, "", -1);
               }
 
               function CreateCookie (name, value, days) { 
                   if (days) {
                       var date = new Date();
                       date.setTime(date.getTime() + (days * 24 * 60 * 60 * 1000));
                       var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString();
                   }
                   else var expires = "";
                   document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/";
               }
               function ReadCookie (name) {
                   var nameEQ = name + "=";
                   var ca = document.cookie.split(';');
                   for (var i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
                       var c = ca[i];
                       while (c.charAt(0) == ' ') c = c.substring(1, c.length);
                       if (c.indexOf(nameEQ) == 0) return c.substring(nameEQ.length, c.length);
                   }
                   return null;
               }
           </script>

                         service = priv.specialty.val();
                     }
 
                     if (priv.address.val() != "" && priv.address.val() != "Address, City or ZIP") {
                         address = priv.address.val();
                     }
 
                     if (priv.state.val() != "" && priv.state.val() != "State" && priv.state.val() != null) {

                     }
 
                     if (priv.radius.val() != "" && priv.radius.val() != "Radius" && priv.radius.val() != null) {

                     if (priv.name.val() != "" && priv.name != "Doctor Name" && priv.name != "Clinic Name") {
                         name = priv.name.val().replace(/'/g, '%27').replace(/\//g, '');
                     }
